{"tid":1221651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍將領：香港既階級成分比臺灣更壞","createTime":"2019-06-14T09:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T12:18:49.000Z","uid":40216,"like":168,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"654d9f86f32b0fba0eb3f96b01db83021686d84c","tid":1221651,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:08:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Jkylebass/status/1139196688432803842（有英文字幕）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJkylebass%2Fstatus%2F1139196688432803842%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%89%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E5%B9%95%EF%BC%89&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=01108374\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJkylebass%2Fstatus%2F1139196688432803842%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%89%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E5%B9%95%EF%BC%89&h=43d378e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Jkylebass/status/1139196688432803842（有英文字幕）</a><br />\n重點節錄：<br />\n毛主席說，你要分析一個社會你得分析一個社會的階級成分<br />\n臺灣有80%的原住民對共產黨是無所謂的，剩下的20%是抓壯丁去的<br />\n可是香港不一樣<br />\n香港有三分一是受港英教育的原住民，他們有一點傲氣，但是和中國沒有什麽仇恨<br />\n可是另外的三分之一是最壞的，1949年到1950年被共產黨清算掃著門口出去的，對共產黨有刻骨仇恨<br />\n剩下的三分一是難民偷渡，會對你共產黨印象好嗎？<br />\n所以回歸以後一個大失誤現在總結，就是一切也不變，不去殖民化行嗎？<br />\n<br />\n有英文字幕希望大家積極透過唔同媒體轉載<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 香港民族骨幹，最壞的三分之一揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屬於最壞既三分之一<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屬於難民或者和中國沒有仇恨的三分之一"},{"pid":"83a39972766d9a47f9fed6244f98e8b54b1d28ab","tid":1221651,"uid":29080,"like":124,"dislike":1,"score":123,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/ngai-26_L3byr_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fngai-26_L3byr_120